Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: 24th at Camelback offers a prime business address in a business park location. Its prominent, enduring architecture provides a strong corporate identity. Features include CAT 5 cabling and ISDN, Wired Gold Certification, 24-hour security, and landscaped gardens. It also offers impressive views over the Biltmore Resort, Piestewa Peak, and The Camby. There is simple and convenient in-and-out parking for the building. The site is easily accessible from I-10, I-17, and SR-60 and by public transportation, and is approximately 10 minutes from Sky Harbor International Airport. The property is also close to the Phoenix Convention and Visitors Bureau, Camelback Mountain, and various office complexes including the Esplanade. There are banking, retail, personal services, and 21 restaurants within walking distance. The building also features an on site restaurant, Scramble.
